{"tid":1703761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何對抗蛇齋餅粽","createTime":"2019-11-10T12:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T12:07:00.000Z","uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2aef17e9d45cf7fcd6ed6936e191b7072b021ba4","tid":1703761,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"相信大家屋企都有廢老收左蛇齋餅粽去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老一輩覺得收左人嘅禮物就要幫返人，呢樣野我地改變唔倒<br />\n但係我地可以做嘅係利用佢地另一樣改變唔倒嘅野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貪念</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地只要同啲廢老解釋返奶共班狗派野嘅目的就係要贏選舉，而佢地輸左嘅話嚟緊幾年就會派更多野想贏返下次選舉，咁班貪心嘅廢老就會自動波唔投奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多位孝順嘅子孫唔係唔幫手呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5091cf2a961b72d88e63304e05ba78d97bb5f7","tid":1703761,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:04:39.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔倒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c887742f909e9872b12812e67de3624f6ba8f14a","tid":1703761,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"差幾日甩p再返嚟推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}